<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>实力拍</title>
	<meta name="keywords" content="实力拍, 人才拍卖">
	<meta name="description" content="实力拍是深圳市红领巾网络科技有限公司旗下的项目">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="email=no">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="../css/img/logo_ico.ico">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/mobile/global.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/mobile/signup.css">
	
	<script src="../js/common/zepto.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/mobile/uiservice.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/mobile/signup.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="viewport">
		<div class="top-bar">
			<span class="bar-title">注册</span>
		</div>
		<div class="sign-wrap">
			<div class="sign-form">
				<div class="inp-item">
					<input type="text" id="email" placeholder="邮箱"/>
				</div>
				<div class="inp-item">
					<input type="password" id="pwd" placeholder="密码"/>
					<span class=""></span>
				</div>
				<div class="inp-item mgn-1 job">
					<input type="text" id="skill" readonly="true" placeholder="专业技能"/>
					<span class="angle"></span>
				</div>
				<div class="inp-item mgn-1 job">
					<input type="text" id="city" readonly="true" placeholder="目标城市"/>
					<span class="angle"></span>
				</div>
				<div class="inp-item comp">
					<input type="text" id="name" placeholder="联系人姓名"/>
				</div>
				<div class="inp-item comp">
					<input type="text" id="title" placeholder="职位"/>
				</div>
				<div class="inp-item mgn-2">
					<input type="text" id="phone" placeholder="手机号"/>
					<span class="send-btn">获取验证码</span>
				</div>
				<div class="inp-item">
					<input type="text" id="code" placeholder="短信验证码"/>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="btn-group">
				<span class="btn" id="submit">注册</span>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="tip-wrap">
			<div class="text">
				<p>恭喜你已经注册成功，请用PC登录实力拍验证邮箱提交简历，参加拍卖，谢谢。</p>
			</div>
			<div class="logo">
				<img class="ico" src="../css/img/app_slp_bg.png"/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
